content.comment:
Is it possible that equation (2) should read

  o_{i} = \sum_{j\in P_{i}} \exp{(q_{i} \cdot k_{j} - z(i, P_{i}))v_{j}}

i.e., that k_{i} should be k_{j}?  Same question for the repeated occurrences of equation (2) in the paper.

